reviewText: I have yet too watch any of these movies but one will very soon.
Purchased this as a gift for my father in law. He loved it! Brought back a lot of memories for him !
This was the perfect gift for my 23 year old son.  He loves westerns.  He and my husband loved watching Westerns over the holiday!!!
My father In Law was in fifth heaven when he received these movies. I was in shocked when I moticed the price for the set, I couldn't resist it.

THE GREAT AMERICAN WESTERN LIMITED EDITION neatly combines the first 20 volumes of this massive collection into one neat package. With over eighty movies (plus a few documentaries), you'll have many weeks of rip roarin' action ahead of you with this one! For a DVD set of similar dimensions, WESTERN CLASSICS 100 MOVIE PACK can't be beat! It has some of these titles, plus a whole lot more. . The following alphabetized program list includes 1 to 10 viewer poll ratings for each film, plus country of origin (if other than USA), years of release and their principal actors.
